9 shall not be treated as separate entities. Each individual shall be
10 charged with his or her personal debt plus the debt of every partnership
11 in which he or she is a partner, except that for purposes of this section
12 (a) an individual shall only be charged with the debt of any limited
13 partnership in which he or she is a partner to the extent that the terms
14 of the limited partnership agreement provide that such individual is to
15 be held liable for the debts or actions of such limited partnership and
16 (b) no individual shall be charged with the debt of any general
17 partnership in which he or she is a partner beyond the extent to which
18 (i) his or her liability for such partnership debt is limited by the
