5 institution. Such an account may also include a line of credit which a
6 financial institution has agreed to extend to its customer;
7 (c) Affiliate financial institution means any financial institution
8 which is a subsidiary of the same bank holding company;
9 (d) Automatic teller machine usage fee means any per transaction fee
10 established by a switch or otherwise established on behalf of an
11 establishing financial institution and collected from the user financial
12 institution and paid to the establishing financial institution for the
13 use of the automatic teller machine. An automatic teller machine usage
14 fee shall not include switch fees;
