26 and any employees, agents, officers, and directors of the financial
27 institution and its bank holding company, if any, shall be immune from
28 any civil, criminal, or administrative liability that may otherwise exist
29 (a) for delaying or refusing to execute a transaction, withdrawal, or
30 disbursement, or for not delaying or refusing to execute such
31 transaction, withdrawal, or disbursement under this section and (b) for
-41-

LB717 LB717
